Subscribe to the Kobui's pose data

>> roslaunch kobuki_node minimal.launch --screen
>> ./odom_subsriber.py

Provide a navigation goal - For single use only
 1. launch the navigation stack program
 2. instead of rviz launch :
    ./simple_navigation_goals.py


Provide a sequence of nav goals:
1. launch navigation stack
2. roslaunch simple_nav_goals movebase_seq.launch


Provide a sequence of nav goals through code (Not launch file)

1. launch navigation stack 
2. ./navigation_patrol


or
1. source and run navigation stack or
roscore,  rosrun turtlebot_stage turtlebot_in_stage.launch

2. ./navigation_patrol.py
